Description: ASUS ZenBook Duo keyboard and platform utilities
 CLI tools for ASUS ZenBook Duo / Pro Duo laptops: keyboard brightness,
 hotkeys, platform profile, ScreenPad, fan control, and sleep/resume hooks.
 .
 This package installs userspace scripts only. The optional out-of-tree
 hid-asus kernel module is not built here; see kernel/README.md upstream.
 .
 Plasma 6 System Settings integration (KCM) is not included in this binary;
 build plasma/kcm separately on Ubuntu 24.04+ (see packaging/debian/README.md).
